    title facebook.tracking.exposed RealityCheck 

  body(onload="initialize();")

    div.container-fluid.realitycontainer.headerborders
      span.col-md-5.right.text-info
        b Here are some of the data! 
        |  We want aggregate a community capable of doing less than a glimpse of the analysis Facebook can do: in humanistic, journalistic, algorithmic, and political fields. Making this ability mainstream is the first awareness.

      span.col-md-1
      span.col-md-6 Our visualization sucks, right? We are unfunded and with a small set of volunteers. If you find a smart way to display how Facebook algorithm distorts the perceived reality, get in touch.
        br
        b Art? Comics? Graph? Papers?
        |  We're open with anything who can make accessible this topic to a larger audience than our bubble.

    nav.navbar.navbar-default
      div.container
        div.navbar-header
          button.navbar-toggle.collapsed(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#thenavbar" aria-expanded="false")
            span(id="sr-only") Toggle navigation
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar

        div.collapse.navbar-collapse(id="thenavbar")
          ul.nav.navbar-nav
            li
              a.switch#diet Information diet
            li
              a.switch#data Raw data
            li
              a.switch#csv CSV
            li
              a.switch#knowmore Know more
            // li
              // a.switch#publications Publications
            li
              a(href="/") Project homepage

    .container-fluid
      .loader-container
        h3 Loading…
        img(class="logo-background" src="/images/fbtrex_logo.svg")

    .container-fluid
      .pageSection#dietSection.hidden
        p.text
          b What feeds you during your navigation? 
          | Maybe you think your 500 fiends are 500 diverse observation points of the world. 
          b Don't give it for granted
          |, Facebook algorithm play in the middle. In your case, we recorder in the last 7 days 
          span#dietSourcesNumber
          |  different sources,
          b  display below
          |. Do you think it is a complete 
          b informative diet
          |?
        #dietGraph

    .container-fluid
      .pageSection#dataSection.hidden
        p This is a list of the data sent to us. If something is missing, probably it is a problem: let us know
        div#contributionBlock
        div#shiftContributionBlock(onclick="loadNextHTMLs('#contributionBlock');")
          b Load Next 100…

    .container-fluid
      .pageSection#csvSection.hidden
        include csv

    .container-fluid
      .pageSection#knowMoreSection.hidden
        include knowmore

    .container-fluid
      .pageSection#publicationSection.hidden
        include publications

